{"title":"Rise Above and Ride Upright with Surly Bikes’ New BMX-Inspired, Sunset Bar","link":"https://bikerumor.com/surly-bikes-new-bmx-inspired-sunset-bar/","date":1715007161000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-Hero.jpeg\" width=\"900\" height=\"779\" alt=\"(Photos/Surly Bikes)\" /></p>\n<p>Wheelie poppers rejoice! The new <a href=\"https://surlybikes.com/parts/sunset_bar\" target=\"_blank\">Sunset Bar</a> handlebar from the Minnesota bike deviants, Surly Bikes, is both wide (820mm) and tall (110mm rise). This new bar resembles a huge, wide BMX bar that would be perfect for cyclists who prefer an upright riding position. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370.jpeg\"><img width=\"890\" height=\"494\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370.jpeg\" alt=\"Surly Sunset Bar compare with SunRise bar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370.jpeg 890w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370-297x165.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370-120x67.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-compare-with-SunRise-bar-e1714842785370-768x426.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Surly Bikes)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The New Sunset Bars are a play on the earlier <a href=\"https://surlybikes.com/parts/sunrise_handlebar\" target=\"_blank\">Sunrise Bars</a> that Surly released back in 2019. But, when Surly set out to make this bar with more back sweep, upsweep, and rise. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"248\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825.jpeg\" alt=\"Surly Sunset Bar with shims\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825-297x74.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825-120x30.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-with-shims-e1714842917825-768x190.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Being upright and durable, this bar would be great for that old 90s MTB with low stack height or a low steer tube that you’ve been eyeballin’ in the corner of the garage. Or even for a bike put together solely with spare parts out of the “magic parts bin” in the other corner of the garage. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"388\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528.jpeg\" alt=\"Surly Sunset Bar side shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528-297x115.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528-120x47.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-side-shot-e1714842848528-768x298.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Sunrise Bar Details</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Sunset Bar is constructed with 4130 Chromoly Custom-Butted Steel tubing for enhanced strength and comfort. It’s finished in an anti-rust Black ED coat for a long product life. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bringing comfort, style, and durability using a more upright position that boasts 110mm of rise. In addition, the bar also has 22 degrees of back sweep, with 14 degrees of up sweep. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Sunset Bar is tested to comply with ASTM 3 and ISO Mountain Standards for “rowdy trail riding and beyond”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"210\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142.jpeg\" alt=\"Surly Sunset Bar straight on\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142-297x62.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142-120x25.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Surly-Sunset-Bar-straight-on-e1714842894142-768x161.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Specifications and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $75</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Material:</strong> Post-weld heat-treated Chromoly Steel</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Clamp Diameter:</strong> 22.2mm; Includes shims for 31.8mm clamp</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Width:</strong> 820mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rise:</strong> 110mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sweep Angle:</strong> 22-degree back sweep, 14-degree upsweep</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> 827g including shims</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>See more bikes, parts, and chaos at the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://surlybikes.com/\">SurlyBikes.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/surly-bikes-new-bmx-inspired-sunset-bar/\">Rise Above and Ride Upright with Surly Bikes’ New BMX-Inspired, Sunset Bar</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2e057b601ca2d4fac120d091c21b3b91f821ced1b4595368536a2d78c7801a7a","category":"Cycling"}